      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANNIHILATING (1) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing third (20.18) and beaten 4.5 lengths over 350m at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Expected to feature in the finish again. QUICK BISCUIT (3) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and two minors from 15 tries. Hit the frame latest (25.58) when second at this track in a Mix 1/2/3. Among the main chances. ROCKY PEPPER (2) turned in a plain performance last time when seventh at this track over 350m behind Sheezel (20.46) in a Mix 1/2/3. Was in the money prior to that. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Should be about the money. MILO DAVIS (7) has strong claims after a top-three finish from this box last time out.",
